Python Package Updates
-----------------------

Requirements
-------------

sudo apt-get install python3-setuptools   |  Bunlardan emin değilim.  
sudo apt-get install python3-distutils    |  Ama yüklemekte zarar yok.
sudo apt-get install python3-pip
sudo apt-get install python3.6-dev
sudo apt-get install python3.7-dev
sudo apt-get install libgirepository1.0-dev libpq-dev python-dev libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev libldap2-dev libsasl2-dev libffi-dev libcups2-dev libcairo2-dev

Packages
---------

sudo python3.7 -m pip install alembic asn1crypto Babel blinker certifi chardet cryptography defer distro-info Flask Flask-BabelEx Flask-Gravatar Flask-HTMLmin Flask-Login Flask-Mail Flask-Migrate Flask-Paranoid Flask-Principal Flask-Security Flask-SQLAlchemy Flask-WTF htmlmin httplib2 idna itsdangerous Jinja2 keyring keyrings.alt launchpadlib lazr.restfulclient lazr.uri louis macaroonbakery Mako MarkupSafe netifaces oauth olefile paramiko passlib pexpect Pillow pip protobuf psutil psycopg2 pyasn1 pycairo pycrypto pycups pygobject pyinotify pymacaroons PyNaCl pyOpenSSL pyRFC3339 python-apt python-debian pytz pyxdg PyYAML reportlab requests requests-unixsocket SecretStorage setuptools simplejson six SQLAlchemy sqlparse sshtunnel systemd-python urllib3 virtualenv wadllib Werkzeug wheel WTForms zope.interface --upgrade
(... python3.7... kısmını python3 olarak da yapın)


VirtualEnv
-----------

pip install virtualenv
cd <virtualenv yaratilacak klasor>
virtualenv -p python<versiyon {3, 3.7}> <isim>
source <isim>/bin/activate
pip<versiyon {3, 3.7}> install <paketler>  veya  pip<versiyon {3.7, 3}> install -r requirements.txt
deactivate
